Smoothie for hormone & gut health 🩷 

Wearing my new favourite workout set from @kicaactive it’s so cute & comfy and I loveee the color! 

🩵 blend together 1 frozen banana, 4 chopped dates, 1/4 avocado & 1 cup homemade almond milk!

💙 line glass with yogurt & blue spirulina powder

💚 pour blended mixture into glass & its ready!

This is my favourite pre-workout smoothie because it’s packed with healthy fats & fiber, natural sugars & fast digesting carbs 🍌🥛 🥑

Nutrition tips for college students 🤓 

1. Learn a few easy, healthy recipes that you can turn to when you have little time. 🍠🍕 

2. Add protein in whenever you can! Even the simplest meals like pasta can be made higher in protein. 

3. Fiber > protein. Chia pudding is the easiest thing to make - it takes 5mins!

4. Stay hydrated with more than just coffee ☕️🙃
